er process. \r\n7) Computer Operator print to Approval of Plant Lay-out and giving final signature approval for Drugs Licensing Authority, Daman & Diu to final signature. \r\n8) After getting a complete final signature, the computer operator will give issues the licence and giving copy to the firm. \"',	1,	'2024-08-22 17:59:21',	0,	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	0),
(42,	1,	27,	2,	62,	3,	63,	'Wholesale Drug License',	'1,2,3',	'1,2,3',	'1,2',	'',	'2',	'30 days',	'',	'',	'',	'',	'Wholesale  Drugs licence (Grant/Renewal) of Rs. 3000/-',	'\"1) Covering letter, 2) Self Assesed check list of documents, 3) Form – 19. 4) Copy of Ownership of premises/Agreement of leave \r\n& Licence/Lease Agreement./Rent receipt. 5) Copy of Memorandum and Articles of Association. 6) List of Directors, 7) Copy of Plan of Premises/Lay out of location. 8) Certificates of Competent Person/ Super wiser in charge. \r\na)	Copy of Offer of Appointment.\r\nb)	Copy of Consent/Acceptance Letter.\r\nc)	Copy of Experience Certificate.\r\nd)	Copy of Degree Certificate. \r\n       e)   Copy of Marks Statement. \r\n       f) Affidavit of pharmacist. 9) Copy of Power of attorney to sign the documents. 10) Photo Identity proof\"',	'\"1) Application is received with paid challan by the designated clerk who forward the Drugs Licensing Authority, Daman.\r\n2) The Drugs Licensing Authority is forwarded to application for further process in this matter for Drugs Inspector of this department. \r\n3) If any entry in form is invalid/not correct/ not supported by the attached documents or any attached documents is not readable or correct or not complying with the provisions of Drugs & Cosmetics Act, 1940 and Rules thereunder, the Drugs Inspector of Daman & Diu will send to the user for compliance. \r\n4) After getting a complete application/compliance, the Drugs Inspector of Drugs Control Department, is inspected /visited by the firm and necessary compliance verification is check out and giving report for compliance if any. And also submitted file to Drugs Licensing Authority, Daman & Diu. \r\n5) If in case any observation regarding inspection, then Drugs Licensing Authority to issued memorandum to firm for further compliance and verification. \r\n6) The firm will compliance report will submitted and Drugs Inspector of verified the documents and the Drugs Inspector is giving approval for further process.\r\n7)  Computer Operator print to licence for validity and giving final signature approval for Drugs Licensing Authority, Daman & Diu to final signature. \r\n8) After getting a complete final signature, the computer operator will give issues the licence copy to the firm.\"',	1,	'2024-08-22 18:00:37',	0,	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	0),
(43,	1,	27,	2,	62,	3,	63,	'Granting of Drug Manufacturing License',	'1,2,3',	'1,2,3,4',	'1,2',	'',	'2',	'30 days',	'',	'',	'',	'',	'Grant/Renewal of Drugs Manufacturing licnece in each FORM Rs. 7500/-',	'\"1) Covering letter alongwith payment of application fees, 2) Self Assesed check list of documents, 3) Form 24 & 27 (Maximum 10 Products should apply under each form), 4) Product List.	5) List of Excipients. 6) Similar Product. 7) Draft Label 8) Method of Analysis.	9) Additional Information Form, 10) Copy of Memorandum of Articles 11) List of Directors with address 12) Copy of Power of attorney to sign the documents. 13)Copy of Plan approval 14) Noc/Consent from SSI, Pollution.\"',	'\"1) The designated /Inward clerk will accept the application and will forward to the Drugs Inspector.\r\n 2) The Drugs Inspector will examine the attached documents and study the plant lay-out as per the guidelines of Schedule –M of the Drugs & Cosmetics Rules, 1945. And if any deficiency in documents or any observations then will convey to the applicant for necessary rectification. \r\n3) After the compliance of observations of Drugs Inspector, the application will be forwarded to the Drugs Licensing Authority for approval. \r\n4) The Drugs Licensing Authority after the compliance will issue /approve the Plant Lay-out with his/her signature. \r\n5) After the approval of Plant Lay-out the applicant with following documents and necessary application fee will apply for the grant/renewal of Drugs Manufacturing Licence.\r\n6) The designated /Inward clerk will accept the application and will forward to the Drugs Inspector. \r\n7) The Drugs Inspector will Scrutiny the application and will inspect factory premises.\r\n8) The Drugs Inspector will convey to the applicant, if any deficiencies in documents and observation of inspection.\r\n9) After the compliance of observations the Drugs Inspector will forward the application to Drugs Licensing Authority.\r\n10) After the Compliance the Drugs Licensing Authority will grant the licence with his/her signature.\"',	1,	'2024-08-22 18:01:51',	0,	'0000-00-00 00:00:00',	0);
